definitions.definition: A female given name from Ancient Greek , an Italian diminutive of Angela .

main_definition: A female given name from Ancient Greek , an Italian diminutive of Angela .

definitions.definition: A young, inexperienced hobo (of either gender).

A female denizen of Los Angeles . Alternative form of Angelena ( “ a female resident of Los Angeles ” ) ; feminine of Angelino ( “ a male resident of Los Angeles ” ) ; Synonym of Angelino / Angeleno ( “ a resident of Los Angeles of either gender ” ) ;
